{"tid":789565,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"法新社闢謠：C朗並未給印度洪災捐款，77億盧比援助傳聞不實","createTime":"2018-08-22T10:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T16:47:19.000Z","uid":20634,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3c4ce5dd11cc36e7fb67c7660ac2ed23ab7f6299","tid":789565,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:39:53.000Z","msg":"據法新社發自印度的消息稱，C羅並未給印度喀拉拉邦洪災的災民們捐過款。此前，推特上有不明來源的傳言稱C羅向洪災災區捐款77億盧比(約合1.1億美元)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.dongqiudi.com/fastdfs3/M00/4E/95/ChOxM1t9H1iAPHgbAAGbx_ERwMM241.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.dongqiudi.com%2Ffastdfs3%2FM00%2F4E%2F95%2FChOxM1t9H1iAPHgbAAGbx_ERwMM241.jpg&h=11a9bd24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印度喀拉拉邦近日遭遇了百年不遇的特大洪災，目前已造成400餘人遇難，數万人因洪災流離失所。在災難發生後，也有一些未經證實的流言在社交網絡上傳播，除了一些誇大災情製造恐慌的傳聞，還包括了一條足壇巨星C羅捐款77億盧比的消息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.dongqiudi.com/fastdfs3/M00/4E/96/ChOxM1t9ILyAbdG_AAERqk2Ibzk135.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.dongqiudi.com%2Ffastdfs3%2FM00%2F4E%2F96%2FChOxM1t9ILyAbdG_AAERqk2Ibzk135.jpg&h=0263fb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n類似的傳言在推特上流傳不少<br />\n<br />\n不過法新社在經過求證之後否認了這一傳聞，這一切其實是始於推特網友在網上請求C羅幫助的推文，並且不久之後又有推文稱C羅已經為災民們提供了大量援助。而在印度一家真相查證網站(Boomlive.in)顯示，很多人在藉用C羅的&ldquo;捐款&rdquo;來指責印度政府面對災害時的處理不力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.dongqiudi.com/fastdfs3/M00/4E/96/ChOxM1t9INeADKukAACLLvUzqNM646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.dongqiudi.com%2Ffastdfs3%2FM00%2F4E%2F96%2FChOxM1t9INeADKukAACLLvUzqNM646.jpg&h=b1433b38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n也有網友表示這一傳聞不可信並調侃稱印度總統莫迪還捐了100億盧比呢<br />\n<br />\n目前，C羅或是他名下的慈善組織並未回應過是否有為喀拉拉邦洪災災區進行捐款。不過在災難發生過後，一些巴塞羅那和利物浦等球隊的球迷組織曾在社交媒體向災區表示關心並號召球迷們給予力所能及的幫助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.dongqiudi.com/fastdfs3/M00/4E/96/ChOxM1t9IV-APiE_AAI0db-lPzw922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.dongqiudi.com%2Ffastdfs3%2FM00%2F4E%2F96%2FChOxM1t9IV-APiE_AAI0db-lPzw922.jpg&h=8d56d9fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地利物浦球迷會發起的援助號召"},{"pid":"5d981c8dc2f06fecc56274413e9e45023b2fbf05","tid":789565,"uid":180462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:41:53.000Z","msg":"所謂慈善球玉真係靠唔字<br />\n要靠我地慈善球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3063355fd4c186bad4147ff9bd505b008bea2788","tid":789565,"uid":5549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:43:51.000Z","msg":"C朗同成龍一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b20be945d33147742e19463c9d7b21a1f8d0eb9","tid":789565,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:45:40.000Z","msg":"朗迷夾錢代捐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97e3d129e01288964c2e8e96fd0d78047c7b102","tid":789565,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:47:49.000Z","msg":"都唔係山區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7acb00007639ed164bdffc359ffbdaa17774c0e7","tid":789565,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:03:01.000Z","msg":"迫害我朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb9364176411b549ae2aadac1002ac06bfe73c8","tid":789565,"uid":30510,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:04:46.000Z","msg":"放流料之後話人地唔捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死乞衣同搶有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67edf46994901bca162f73f15884d7a1c7ab6156","tid":789565,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"照咁計連登個毅進星咪一鳩樣"},{"pid":"80ae74f53f18c8203308a1f0cdc6bc4b8dfbc81c","tid":789565,"uid":35176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:19:31.000Z","msg":"屌年年都有啦 有邊一年C朗係冇捐錢新聞不實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zz